Health and RehabilitationProperties Trust said it declared its initial dividend of 55cts per share for the quarter ending March 31, 1987.    The dividend is payable May 20 to shareholders of recordApril 20, 1987, it said.    The dividend includes five cts attributable to the periodbetween Dec 23 and 31, 1986, and 50 cts attributable to thefirst quarter of 1987, ending March 31, 1987. Reuter&#3;